description:
Following yesterdays story of a man having surgery to be taller - Dr. Debipershad - who performed the surgery calls in to discuss the procedure, and answer Bobby and Amy's questions. Round 2 of survivor style - name that Disney movie after hearing this song is here. Caller needs advice on spending more time with kids or taking more money
